node.text: She’s okay. I’m the midwife. She’s here to have a baby.” Officer, “Do I help you?” Midwife “No, she’s here to have a baby.” I love how this mom stops and knows to listen to her body, and I love how that midwife multitasks catching and talking to police and then passes the babe through moms legs effortlessly. Video originally from @naturalbirthworks
